reviewText: I never thought I'd see this video show again! I rented this when I was 12 and 13 from my local video rental store and LOVED the cars presented here from the Cobras to the custom slant nosed Porsches (Good luck seeing any of those around today) and that Turbo CarTech Mustang. Now, it and another Exotic Cars Of The World VHS tape sit proudly in my collection.
